# Build output belongs in dist/, never in src/. Compiled .js/.d.ts committed into
# src/ silently shadow their .tsx sources when Remotion's webpack resolves the
# NodeNext './x.js' imports — which once dropped the VideoStitch composition from
# the bundle. Keep src/ pure TypeScript.
dist/
src/**/*.js
src/**/*.jsx
src/**/*.d.ts
src/**/*.d.ts.map
src/**/*.js.map
